Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:02.17,中文,,0,0,0,,《吸血鬼日记》前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Previously on "The Vampire Diaries"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:03.61,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:06.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我想你催眠我 让我忘记我曾经爱过他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want you to compel me to forget that I ever loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:07.34,中文,,0,0,0,,谁是达蒙·塞尔瓦托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who is Damon Salvatore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.54,中文,,0,0,0,,他就是个禽兽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.02,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我女朋友艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my girlfriend Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.12,中文,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上有人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Somebody killed her last night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:12.69,中文,,0,0,0,,就当着我面杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.19,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了恩佐也不能让她起死回生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Killing Enzo won't bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:15.26,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我杀了他 我就能安心离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I kill him, I can leave this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.49,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I can start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我想用我的方式杀死他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have my own way I like them to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.28,0:00:23.74,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼都进不了神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Vampires can't get into Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.51,中文,,0,0,0,,可他们能在附近埋伏着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They can lurk around the borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你袭击并催眠的那个女孩 莎拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sarah-- the girl you attacked and you compelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:28.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:30.26,中文,,0,0,0,,她知道我是什么生物了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Knows what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈住在神秘瀑布镇很多年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My mom lived in Mystic Falls for years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.83,中文,,0,0,0,,生我之前就住那儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before she had me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们到底在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.71,中文,,0,0,0,,1994年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1994.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:38.85,中文,,0,0,0,,该死 我们永远都出不去了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My own hell. We're never getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.72,中文,,0,0,0,,还有其他人在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's someone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.86,中文,,0,0,0,,火焰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Incendia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在是一条绳上的蚂蚱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你是不是一直都是猪队友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you always try and kill your teammates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.66,中文,,0,0,0,,重要的是你重新拥有了魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The important thing is that you have your magic back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.60,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你的魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because your magic is the key
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是我们逃出去的关键\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to getting the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是闯进了总统办公室\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And of course, I broke into the oval office
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.95,中文,,0,0,0,,拍了张在窗边眺望肯尼迪机场的照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and took a picture of myself at the window looking all J.F.K.,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:05.02,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我想 天啊 等下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but then I was like, "Wait. How am I gonna get
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:06.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我要怎么才能把照片发送出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}these photos developed?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:08.51,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 只回答那个该死的问题就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, my god! Just answer the damn question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要怎么离开这个隔世之地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How are we gonna get out of this twilight zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我有个问题要问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got a question for you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.82,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么你觉得我们就被困在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why do you think we're stuck on a repeating loop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.69,中文,,0,0,0,,1994年5月10号这一天呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of May 10, 1994,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:18.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就注定永远要这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}doomed to relive a solar eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:20.22,中文,,0,0,0,,重复着日食这一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}forever and ever and ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我特么怎么会知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How the hell should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:22.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到你对邦妮说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I heard you tell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:23.81,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你个人的地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bonnie this place was your own personal hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:25.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我很好奇是为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm kind of curious why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我找到了你要的所有东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I found everything you asked for--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:29.25,中文,,0,0,0,,开瓶器 地漏 砂轮 果酱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}can opener, shower drain, grinding wheel, jam,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:33.19,中文,,0,0,0,,小刀 百科全书的O列表\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}pocket knife, volume "O" Of the encyclopedia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.63,中文,,0,0,0,,一片指甲和一只黑色马克笔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a nail, and a black marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.96,中文,,0,0,0,,现在呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:41.70,中文,,0,0,0,,手都绑上了怎么告诉你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't show you with my hands taped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.20,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.43,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.58,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 你现在能说了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Fine. How's this pile of crap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.98,中文,,0,0,0,,这堆破烂东西有什么用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}gonna get us out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.18,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你在1994年5月10号做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll explain as soon as you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我立刻就告诉你们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what you did on May 10, 1994?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这有什么差别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这么说吧 邦妮的魔法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Put it this way. Bonnie's magic is one part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.45,中文,,0,0,0,,是解决问题的一部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.93,中文,,0,0,0,,而我悬而未决的问题是另一部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My as yet undisclosed knowledge is the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.33,中文,,0,0,0,,也就是说你不用做什么就能回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which means you would be hitching a ride home for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:08.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道你值不值得我费工夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just want to know if you deserve to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,或者我可以折磨你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or I could just torture you until
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.94,中文,,0,0,0,,直到你说出你的方法为止\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you say something useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.51,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你折磨我 我会发疯的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you torture me, I'll get mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:15.11,中文,,0,0,0,,那样的话我就不会想帮你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then I won't want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.15,中文,,0,0,0,,他是有多弱智\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What kind of person needs to have that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.65,中文,,0,0,0,,还需要解释的这么直白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}explained to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.63,中文,,0,0,0,,态度好点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Play nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.03,中文,,0,0,0,,别想着能和他发展\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stop trying to impress the new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.63,中文,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不直接告诉他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why don't you just tell him your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.99,中文,,0,0,0,,也许是因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe because I don't want to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想说我做过的最恶劣的事 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}about the worst thing I ever did, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:33.27,中文,,0,0,0,,得了 我现在在听\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ooh. Now I'm listening.
