Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:50.35,话,,0,0,0,,视频字幕由 {\fs60\c&HFF8ED9&}SSK字幕组{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\fs50} 制作发布\N字幕只供学习 请勿做任何商业行为\N   敬请关注新浪微博@SSK字幕组\N合作贴吧：吸血鬼日记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:44.74,中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:47.08,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好听恐怖故事了么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ready for some bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.00,中文,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unh. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我们快50年没见了 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I barely seen you in 50 years, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.43,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以邀请你的哥哥进去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You could invite a brother in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.87,中文,,0,0,0,,给我个理由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Give me one good reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.07,中文,,0,0,0,,去听下你的电话留言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Check your answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.50,中文,,0,0,0,,我在试着和你重启友谊新篇章\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm trying to turn over a new leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到你的留言了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, I heard your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我还听说你给莱西送花了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I also heard you sent Lexi some flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.05,中文,,0,0,0,,在你让她房顶上被烧死的17年后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}17 years after you left her to burn to death on a rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.45,中文,,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.45,中文,,0,0,0,,确实有点迟 不过呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a little late, but I see you're
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.55,中文,,0,0,0,,我看到了你的诚意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}trying to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我只想知道原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I just want to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.82,中文,,0,0,0,,这个我可以告诉你 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ugh. Well, I can tell you this, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我厌倦了在纽约撕逼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm tired of tearing up New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.86,中文,,0,0,0,,也许是因为趴体 也许是我良心发现了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe it's the partying, maybe it's my conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:23.36,中文,,0,0,0,,那也得有个良心才行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I believe that would require one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.23,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我突然有那么一瞬的清醒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And then I had this moment of clarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.59,中文,,0,0,0,,想着说 如果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I said, "Wouldn't it be great
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我能每天在自己的床上醒来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"If I just woke up in my own bed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.06,中文,,0,0,0,,有个全新开始 不是更好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and could have a fresh start?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你一定是达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You must be Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.97,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 这是 额 扎克·塞尔瓦托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon, this is, uh, Zach Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.63,中文,,0,0,0,,他是这个房子的主人 他了解家族史\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He owns the house now. He knows the family history,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉他 如果你做了越界的行为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I told him if you got out of line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我会亲自收拾你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd take care of you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么总把我想的那么坏呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why are you always expecting the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.04,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}out of me, Stefan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.84,中文,,0,0,0,,不是啊 我要是真把你想得那么坏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, I don't. Otherwise, I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我就不会让他这么做了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}allow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.21,中文,,0,0,0,,进来吧 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on in, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.82,中文,,0,0,0,,多谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:56.95,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好重新来过了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You ready to start over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.32,中文,,0,0,0,,当然啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hell, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn微软雅黑\fs40\c&HE7E7E8&\pos(618,620)}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,逃跑的姑娘有消息了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Any sign of our runaway girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.06,中文,,0,0,0,,还没 我和卡罗琳都已经\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nope. Caroline and I combed the border
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.20,中文,,0,0,0,,在边界搜寻了3次了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of Mystic Falls 3 times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.63,中文,,0,0,0,,还是没找到萨拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No sign of Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.13,中文,,0,0,0,,公路上也找不到她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's not any of the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.63,中文,,0,0,0,,她可能还待在镇上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which means she's probably in Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.23,中文,,0,0,0,,这就太糟了 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is bad, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.60,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦她跨越边界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her compulsion went away as soon as she
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.34,中文,,0,0,0,,对她的催眠就失效了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}crossed the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.50,中文,,0,0,0,,她知道我和卡罗琳是吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She knows that Caroline and I are vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:24.94,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我得挂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen. I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我 额 晚点再聊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll, uh, talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,额 我要回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Um, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.55,中文,,0,0,0,,萨凡纳不是你的家 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Savannah's not your home, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.48,中文,,0,0,0,,它只是你逃避 藏身之处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's an escape, a hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.79,中文,,0,0,0,,这里才是你的家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn微软雅黑\fs40\c&HB0B3B8&\pos(908,344)}欢迎来到\N神秘瀑布镇 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.19,中文,,0,0,0,,不 这曾经是我的家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. This was my home, but I can no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,但我已经进不了边界了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}enter its borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.56,中文,,0,0,0,,因此 我有个新家了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Therefore, I have a new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.43,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你就心灰意冷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you're just gonna throw in the towel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.13,中文,,0,0,0,,回去过你虚假的新生活吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and go back to your fake new life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我虚假的新生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. My fake new life ended
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:59.77,中文,,0,0,0,,在恩佐杀了我真实的女朋友艾薇后 就结束了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when Enzo decided to kill my not-so-fake girlfriend Ivy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.08,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我要回家 收拾好行李\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I am going to go home, pack up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.58,中文,,0,0,0,,再重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.85,中文,,0,0,0,,然后假装这儿的一切都不存在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}By pretending like your life here never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.15,中文,,0,0,0,,你会发现 忘记过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'd be surprised how easy it is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.62,中文,,0,0,0,,有多容易 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to forget the past, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:12.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我才不信你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你失去了你哥哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You lost your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你不可能假装没事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's no way that you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用担心我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You do not have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我以前又不是没这么做过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not like I haven't done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我有自己的一套方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have a system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.83,中文,,0,0,0,,那就给我看看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Show me. Prove to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,证明它有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that your system works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.64,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我相信你是真的开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I believe that you actually are happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我就放你走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then I'll let you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.68,中文,,0,0,0,,但如果我不认同 虽然我很有可能不会认同\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but if I don't buy it, which I probably won't,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我会一直骚扰你 直到你回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will keep harassing you until you come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:42.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我说的可是 类似 恩佐 那程度的烦恼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I'm talking about, like, Enzo-sized harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,同意吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.23,中文,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.10,中文,,0,0,0,,那个逃跑的女孩 莎拉 怎么办\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And what about our runaway girl Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.70,中文,,0,0,0,,既然我们进不了神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, we can't step foot in Mystic Falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.54,中文,,0,0,0,,那这事现在就归马特和杰里米管了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so now it's up to Matt and Jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.35,中文,,0,0,0,,好样的 全都吐出来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Attaboy. Get her all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.95,中文,,0,0,0,,他真的还在吐吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is he seriously still wasted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 小废物凌晨4点醉倒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Little punk showed up on my doorstep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.22,中文,,0,0,0,,在我家门口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}last night at 4:00 in the morning drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你们两个一起在找莎拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought you two were looking for Sarah together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我找了 但她显然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I did my part. She is definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.01,中文,,0,0,0,,没有藏在塞尔瓦多的酒柜里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not hiding in the Salvatore liquor cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你那个厌恶吸血鬼的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen. What about your vampire-hating
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.22,中文,,0,0,0,,社区监督队员呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}neighborhood watch guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.82,中文,,0,0,0,,如果莎拉找他求助 那问题就来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If Sarah goes to him for help, that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在在去特里普办公室的路上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm on my way to Tripp's office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我能取得他的信任 让他告诉我他所知道的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think I can get him to trust me and tell me what he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,注意安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.80,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Alaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.30,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.40,中文,,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这是杰里米 杰里米·吉尔伯特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is Jeremy-- Jeremy Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.14,中文,,0,0,0,,他有点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.28,中文,,0,0,0,,-未成年吗 -是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}-Underage? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.78,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我看出来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能给他一些\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was hoping you could give him one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.92,中文,,0,0,0,,快速补给液\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of those rapid rehydration
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,治疗宿醉一类的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}hangover cure type things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.88,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 好的 你是说 我们留给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, yeah. You mean, the ones we reserve
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.79,中文,,0,0,0,,专业运动员和第三世界\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for professional athletes and starving children
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,饥饿的孩子们的那种\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in third-world countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.22,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我想我们先做个完全的检查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. I think we'll start with a full workup--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.56,中文,,0,0,0,,物理 血液 病毒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}physical, blood, toxicology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.97,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 为什么你不顺便加多个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Why don't you throw in an STD screening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.10,中文,,0,0,0,,性病筛查  哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}while you're at it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.94,中文,,0,0,0,,-要这样子吗 -是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}-Really? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.04,中文,,0,0,0,,从走廊下去往右走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Down the hall to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我该问吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do I want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.75,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个神秘学教授\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's just another day in the life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.41,中文,,0,0,0,,生活中的某一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of an occult studies professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.41,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 如果还包括监护喝醉的傻逼的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if that entails supervising drunk morons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:09.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们的共同点可比我想得多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then you and I have a lot more in common than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.21,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 对不起 凯伦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know, and I'm sorry Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,杰伊是个好孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jay was a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我保证 你会第一时间知道消息的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I promise. You'll be the first one to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.39,中文,,0,0,0,,特里普 你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tripp, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.83,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我刚告诉了杰伊的父母\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. I just told Jay's parents
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我是那个发现他们儿子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I was the one who found their son
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.46,中文,,0,0,0,,昨晚死在森林里的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}dead in the woods last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我听说了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道发生了什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.91,中文,,0,0,0,,他和你一起去聚会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He went to the party with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:50.58,中文,,0,0,0,,他喝醉了 我说过要送他回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was drunk. I offered to give him a ride home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他说他要走路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and he said he'd walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我应该开车带他回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I should have driven him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我要去警长那录口供\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm gonna give the sheriff my statement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.98,中文,,0,0,0,,试试弄清楚杰伊发生了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and try to make sense of what happened to Jay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.08,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 也许我应该和你一起去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait. Maybe I should go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:08.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我可能是看到杰伊的最后一个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I might have been the last person to see Jay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:11.66,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 就这样 我们走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Done. Let's take a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我工作时需要有点消遣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to be entertained while I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:20.74,中文,,0,0,0,,地狱的故事 请\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hell story, please
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.74,中文,,0,0,0,,提醒我不要杀死他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Remind me not to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.04,中文,,0,0,0,,也许告诉他你的故事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe telling him your story will take
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.15,中文,,0,0,0,,会转移你的注意力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your mind off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你到底在哪一边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在能回到我们爱的人身边的那一边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The side where get to go home to the people we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.82,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.79,中文,,0,0,0,,1994年五月 我住在这\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In May 1994, I was living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我回家来回归正途\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd come home to walk the straight and narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.63,中文,,0,0,0,,我能喝一口那个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I have a sip of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我很饿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.70,中文,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,哟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.21,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 很不错 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mmm. It's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.47,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.87,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 是吧 我不记得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, yeah. I can't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.51,中文,,0,0,0,,那个松鼠是被车撞死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if that squirrel was roadkill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.11,中文,,0,0,0,,还是我用捕鼠器抓住的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or one I caught in the rat trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.65,中文,,0,0,0,,还是更希望它是被撞死的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Better hope it was roadkill, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.78,中文,,0,0,0,,因为捕鼠器上都是老鼠屎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because the rat trap was full of rat droppings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.25,中文,,0,0,0,,转转你的舌头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Swish your tongue around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.38,中文,,0,0,0,,它感觉像头发 还是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does it feel like hair, or is it more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.38,中文,,0,0,0,,更像粒状的小球\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of a grainy pellet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.36,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你好啊 扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How's it going Zach?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.79,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么去杂货店买这么多东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's up with all the grocery trips?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:14.95,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 家里有个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah. One of the boarders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,想吃蓝莓煎饼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is craving blueberry pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 也许该我来管理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, maybe I should run
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.56,中文,,0,0,0,,塞尔瓦多家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the Salvatore boarding house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.70,中文,,0,0,0,,接过扎克的位置\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take over for Zach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.33,中文,,0,0,0,,和盖尔和睦共处\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}get in good with Gail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.17,中文,,0,0,0,,她在服马鞭草\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's on Vervain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.40,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So is Zach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.16,中文,,0,0,0,,所以 别对他们动手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which means hands off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:34.27,中文,,0,0,0,,太棒辣 我们的救世主是疯的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Perfect. Our savior's insane
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,还得了嗜睡症\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and narcoleptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.48,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 我清醒着呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, no, no. I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.11,中文,,0,0,0,,让我猜猜 你杀了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let me guess-- you killed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.44,中文,,0,0,0,,那个孕妇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.94,中文,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 卡伊 你都没听清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shut up, Kai. You weren't listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我睡着也能听到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was listening in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你和你的远侄扎克出去闲逛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You were hanging out with your distant nephew Zach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.31,中文,,0,0,0,,那个你叫扎克叔叔的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who you called uncle Zach
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.42,中文,,0,0,0,,因为那样没那么混乱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because that's not confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.12,中文,,0,0,0,,加上孕妇盖尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Plus pregnant lady Gail,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.76,中文,,0,0,0,,她成为了你的目标\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who had a big bull's-eye on her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.19,中文,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.89,中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你没有杀死一个孕妇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell me you didn't kill a pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.00,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 绝对就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, that's totally what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:04.93,中文,,0,0,0,,要不然为什么今天会是他的地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why else would today be his personal hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:08.63,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 又来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.23,中文,,0,0,0,,你之所以现在还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The only reason that you're alive right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.80,中文,,0,0,0,,是因为我以为你可以带我们离开这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is because I thought you could get us out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.27,中文,,0,0,0,,能帮助我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you could help us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.97,中文,,0,0,0,,但你没有任何办法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but you don't have any answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:17.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你只是一个满手果酱的幼稚男孩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're just a man-child with jam on your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.64,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 那么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.65,中文,,0,0,0,,想回家 我们需要用到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To get home, we'll harness the power
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.15,中文,,0,0,0,,一件神秘的古物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.98,中文,,0,0,0,,来控制月蚀的能量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}using a mystical relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.65,中文,,0,0,0,,它被称作运星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's called an Ascendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,它看起来长这样 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it looks like this, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们最后拥有它的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The last time we had it was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是在西北太平洋\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the pacific northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.79,中文,,0,0,0,,俄勒冈州\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.26,中文,,0,0,0,,它属于我们家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It belonged to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.69,中文,,0,0,0,,所以给你一点血让你开始动手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So here's a little blood to get you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.69,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们只需要一个定位咒语\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now all we need is a locator spell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.80,中文,,0,0,0,,来找到它的下落\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to pinpoint its whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.02,中文,,0,0,0,,你能带我们出去了吗 邦邦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Think you can find our ticket out here, Bon Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.69,中文,,0,0,0,,见鬼 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hell, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.60,中文,,0,0,0,,她很可爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.34,中文,,0,0,0,,死之前是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.58,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我也是 但都结束了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Me, too, but what's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.95,中文,,0,0,0,,因此在纳完税 交完社保\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So after taxes and social security
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:12.33,中文,,0,0,0,,和医保之后 我还剩206.03 美元\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and health insurance, I'm left with $206.03
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.93,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我这周的生活费了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to spend for the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.23,中文,,0,0,0,,想去喝点酒吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want to get drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.73,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 你连医保都有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan, health insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:22.07,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 为了能重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. The point is to start over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,尽可能去过人类的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}pretend to be as human as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.70,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗 意思是不再用吸血鬼特权\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, ok. So no vampire privileges,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:31.31,中文,,0,0,0,,不再有包袱 不再使用任何从前用过的东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no baggage, nothing from our old lives whatsoever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:33.91,中文,,0,0,0,,那这是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ahem. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.99,中文,,0,0,0,,这你可难倒我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.95,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙不在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See, Damon isn't around
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.15,中文,,0,0,0,,没人叫它老爷车了 所以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to call it a granny mobile, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.26,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 你哥哥确实很喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Your brother really did love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.49,中文,,0,0,0,,给别人起绰号来折磨他们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to torture people with nicknames
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:46.99,中文,,0,0,0,,完全就是为了折磨别人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and just plain torture people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.23,中文,,0,0,0,,可以这么说吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's one way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.26,中文,,0,0,0,,所以把桥烧掉 找份没有前途的工作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So your system for moving on requires
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.83,中文,,0,0,0,,就是你重新开始的办法喽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}both burning bridges and a dead-end job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.67,中文,,0,0,0,,还有更好玩的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We haven't even gotten to the fun part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.73,中文,,0,0,0,,给公共事业捐款吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Paying utilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不是 是决定未来三十年里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Deciding who you want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你想成为什么样的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for the next 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你可能想成为一名宇航员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you want to be an astronaut,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.64,中文,,0,0,0,,想成为奥林匹克运动员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you want to be an Olympic athlete,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.14,中文,,0,0,0,,还想逃医学课程\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you want to skip med school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.21,中文,,0,0,0,,结果 你成为了一名医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}boom, you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.58,中文,,0,0,0,,继续 来挑战我吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go ahead. Challenge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让你知道我是如何实现的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.51,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看你是块什么料\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right. Let's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:12.94,中文,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:17.91,中文,,0,0,0,,那孩子简直就是个酒鬼 要给他输盐水\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Quite a boozer that kid. Put him on a saline drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.61,中文,,0,0,0,,没给他洗胃算是幸运了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's lucky I didn't pump his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.81,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 他这几个月挺不好过的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. You know, he's had a rough couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你把他带到这来就为了给他贴些创可贴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you bring him in here to put a band-aid on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.95,中文,,0,0,0,,再找些借口吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and make some more excuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.14,中文,,0,0,0,,不 其实我是到这来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. I actually came here for some advice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.65,中文,,0,0,0,,寻求专家意见的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}from a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:30.85,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗 揍他一顿就行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, a kick in the ass might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.61,中文,,0,0,0,,杰里米也是一样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jeremy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:33.95,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 如果他像他姐姐一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. If he's anything like his sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我保证他会没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sure he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我还是个学生的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's nothing I don't treat every single night on campus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.12,中文,,0,0,0,,每个晚上在学校我也会这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or didn't do myself when I was a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.19,中文,,0,0,0,,那你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.86,中文,,0,0,0,,以前也是聚会达人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Former party animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.32,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 是的 我以前老是被人从\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, yeah, yeah. I used to get kicked out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.83,中文,,0,0,0,,图书馆赶出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the library all the time, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.66,中文,,0,0,0,,因为马上就关门了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because it was closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.19,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗 专心研究巫术圣经吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right. Head in the Wiccan Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 再给你一个专家建议\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. One more piece of professional advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.65,中文,,0,0,0,,当一个事业有成 又很性感\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When a successful, sexy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.31,中文,,0,0,0,,只是略微有点不自信的医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}only moderately insecure doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,在和你调情的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is flirting with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.38,中文,,0,0,0,,最好不要分散你的注意力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}give her your undivided attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.23,中文,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳在寝室里很低调\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Caroline's laying low at the dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.16,中文,,0,0,0,,没有看到莎拉的踪影\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no sign of Sarah yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.70,中文,,0,0,0,,这意味着她不是藏起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which means she's either hiding out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.21,中文,,0,0,0,,就是在准备在晚间独家新闻上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or she's planning her nightly news exclusive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.37,中文,,0,0,0,,爆我的料\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to out me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.37,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她真的想爆你出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if she does out you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就去别的地方重新开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then you start your life over somewhere else
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.51,中文,,0,0,0,,摆脱所有的 额 超自然破事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}free of all the, uh, supernatural drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.75,中文,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好看我实行我的方法了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you ready to see the system in action?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.59,中文,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.42,中文,,0,0,0,,把戒指给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hand over your ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.42,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你的戒指\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.72,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.71,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜·威廉姆斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Elena Williams...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:11.42,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪 斯特凡·库伯 你在干嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ohh! Stefan Cooper, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:14.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经认识了很长时间了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We've known each other for a very long time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你一直都是我最好的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you've always been my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.87,中文,,0,0,0,,而我一直都在爱着你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have always loved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我想和你共度余生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I want to spend the rest of my life with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.81,中文,,0,0,0,,-你愿意 -等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}-Will you -Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你不会是因为我怀孕了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not just proposing to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.44,中文,,0,0,0,,才向我求婚的吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because I'm pregnant, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.12,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我向你求婚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I-I am proposing to you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.82,中文,,0,0,0,,是因为你就是我的最爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because you are my rock, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你一直都在我身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have stood by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:39.86,中文,,0,0,0,,陪着我一起康复 陪我度过了监狱里的时光\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}through the multiple rehabs, the jail time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.66,中文,,0,0,0,,陪我一起养斗牛时留下的伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the bull fighting injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我是说 是你把我从危险边缘拯救出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, you have brought me back from the edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.46,中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 这个孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and, sweetheart, this baby
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:51.09,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们来说是再美好不过的存在了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is the best thing that ever happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你愿意嫁给我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.35,中文,,0,0,0,,愿意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.56,中文,,0,0,0,,喔 噢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ha! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你太疯狂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aw. You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 新的身份 新的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See that? New identities, new lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.56,中文,,0,0,0,,这很简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.30,中文,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你们 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you all so much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:22.18,中文,,0,0,0,,嘛哩嘛哩哄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Phesmatos tribum nas ex viras,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.07,中文,,0,0,0,,嘛哩嘛哩哄哄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}sequitas sanguinem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.68,中文,,0,0,0,,感觉不对劲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.98,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我需要一个大一点的地图\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe I need a bigger map.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,也许是你技巧生疏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe you're just out of practice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.85,中文,,0,0,0,,现在魔法很烂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you suck at magic now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.49,中文,,0,0,0,,别理他 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ignore him, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.59,中文,,0,0,0,,就当他是一个白噪音机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pretend he's a white noise machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我以前就是这么无视我的兄弟姐妹的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's how I used to tune out my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:42.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我有一大堆的弟弟妹妹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I grew with a ton of little sisters and brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.99,中文,,0,0,0,,他们都在不停地哭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and all of them constantly yammering,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.67,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 额 教会了我如何集中注意力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but it, uh, taught me how to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.87,中文,,0,0,0,,悠着点 大哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Easy there, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.44,中文,,0,0,0,,她还和你不熟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She doesn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.77,中文,,0,0,0,,至少也灌她一杯再说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At least buy her a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我能叫你利兹吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I call you Liz?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.37,中文,,0,0,0,,确定吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你女儿真可爱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your daughter is so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 卡罗琳挺难伺候的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Caroline's high maintenance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.69,中文,,0,0,0,,但这是值得的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but she's worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,一定要扔了这张照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am so getting rid of that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 来给我和扎克拍照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan, come take a picture of Zach and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.10,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.47,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.71,中文,,0,0,0,,现在该继续吃我爱吃的东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And now back to my cravings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:31.59,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 额 你的手腕怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Um, what happened to your wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.69,中文,,0,0,0,,所以这些东西如何帮我们观看日食\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So how does thing help us watch the eclipse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.59,中文,,0,0,0,,你把它放在你和\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You put it in between you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.93,中文,,0,0,0,,那个热辣的无法直视的事物之间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the thing that's too hot to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.33,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 真的有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ahh! It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫会觉得你很有趣的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My husband would get a kick out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我们应该邀请你们找天过来吃饭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We should invite you over to dinner sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.80,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 你对盖尔做了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon, what'd you do to Gail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.01,中文,,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is everything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.97,中文,,0,0,0,,看来这回完蛋了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Looks like the jig is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.17,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:59.54,中文,,0,0,0,,回家 忘记你曾经见过我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go home. Forget you ever met us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.17,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你为什么要吸盖尔的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. How the hell did you feed on Gail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.77,中文,,0,0,0,,她在服马鞭草\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's on Vervain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.88,中文,,0,0,0,,放在她的咖啡里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In her coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我上周调了包\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I swapped it out last week,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.34,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克也一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}same for Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.68,中文,,0,0,0,,这些人都是我的朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}These people are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.21,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克是家人 他们相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Zach is family. They trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.75,中文,,0,0,0,,所以他们会相信我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And they'll trust us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:13.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是在家里吸 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. I'm only feeding inside the house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.65,中文,,0,0,0,,抓住 开吃 清除记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Snatch, eat, erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.31,中文,,0,0,0,,这完全行得通 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's all completely functional, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你这是个新的开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you it's a new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:34.03,中文,,0,0,0,,嘛哩嘛哩轰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}...Nas ex viras, sequitas sanguinem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,嘛哩嘛哩轰轰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Phesmatos tribum nas ex viras,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.40,中文,,0,0,0,,嘛哩嘛哩轰轰轰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}sequitas sanguinem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.50,中文,,0,0,0,,血液正流向弗吉尼亚州\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The blood's moving towards Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.57,中文,,0,0,0,,那不对啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:42.67,中文,,0,0,0,,额 咒语起作用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh-uh. The spell's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.07,中文,,0,0,0,,它指出了神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's showing me Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.74,中文,,0,0,0,,它感觉很\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It feels so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.98,中文,,0,0,0,,接近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.31,中文,,0,0,0,,它就在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:06.87,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是运星吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's the Ascendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.80,中文,,0,0,0,,唯一的一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.71,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的心理游戏 蠢货\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks for the mind games, jackass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.87,中文,,0,0,0,,这只是另一个小测试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was just another little test
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:16.37,中文,,0,0,0,,以确保邦妮的魔法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to make sure Bonnie's magic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.27,中文,,0,0,0,,能足够的精确\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}was precise enough for the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我相信你已经准备好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I do believe you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:23.47,中文,,0,0,0,,收拾好你的行李\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pack your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要回家了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fn微软雅黑\fs40\c&HE7E7E8&\pos(626,660)}神秘瀑布镇  1994年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.65,中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我没弄明白 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So here's what I don't get, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么想方设法地回到我的生活里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why'd you insinuate yourself back into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:52.59,中文,,0,0,0,,然后作弊 撒谎 破坏所有的规则\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then cheat and lie and break all the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.76,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我撒谎是因为我知道你会生气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I lied because I knew you'd be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.73,中文,,0,0,0,,信不信由你 我喜欢呆在这里 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Believe it or not, I like being here, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:05.56,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aah! Auugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.07,中文,,0,0,0,,当你决定好好表现的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'll get your daylight ring back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你会拿回你的日光戒指的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when you decide to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.14,中文,,0,0,0,,现在回答我的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么回到这来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why'd you come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.91,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我想我的弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I missed my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我想有一个可以唤起我人性的人 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted to have a connection to my humanity, Stefan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我想再次感受一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted to feel something again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.72,中文,,0,0,0,,当我决定回家的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and when I decided to come back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这一切都涌上心头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it all came rushing back
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.25,中文,,0,0,0,,就像我希望的那样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just like I hoped it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.45,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 恭喜 现在呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, congrats. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.66,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 伙计 我们一起上路吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, man. Let's just hit the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:29.55,中文,,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.75,中文,,0,0,0,,额 我会让你开我的车\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh? I'll let you drive my car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我会带你脱离素食主义\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll get you off this vegan diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.69,中文,,0,0,0,,再次教你如何填饱肚子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}teach you how to feed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.09,中文,,0,0,0,,那肯定很赞 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It'll be great, Stef.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.43,中文,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.73,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 相信我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on! Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:45.93,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 我可以想象到和你一起公路旅行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. I can imagine a road trip with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.37,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以想象你以吸食那些无辜的人为生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can imagine you feeding on innocent people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:51.70,中文,,0,0,0,,然后留下一堆尸体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and leaving a trail of bodies behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以想象你让我喝人血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can imagine you making me drink human blood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.93,中文,,0,0,0,,当我遭受痛苦时嘲笑我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and laughing at me while I suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你该学会成为乐观主义者 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Way to be an optimist, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我只看到事实 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm just looking at the facts, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:03.53,中文,,0,0,0,,1912年 你说服我再次喝人血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1912, you convinced me to drink human blood again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.63,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是我成了一个开膛手的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}which is why I became a ripper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.27,中文,,0,0,0,,1942年 你几乎再次带我走入岐途\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1942, you almost pushed me off the rails again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:10.40,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你太特么爱折腾了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because you were so damn needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.43,中文,,0,0,0,,1977年 我让我最好的朋友来帮助你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1977, you left my best friend to die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.10,中文,,0,0,0,,而你就丢下她让她死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}after I sent her to come help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.17,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我终于感到快乐了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and now I'm finally happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我有了新生活，我现在过得很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have a new life, I'm doing well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:20.74,中文,,0,0,0,,而你 你就是不能接受那一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and, uh, you just can't handle that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.06,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以吗 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}can you, Damon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是想尝试去搞砸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not trying to screw up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你愚蠢的新生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your dumb new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:26.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用尝试了 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You don't have to try, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.70,中文,,0,0,0,,只要你活在这世上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All you have to do is exist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.03,中文,,0,0,0,,无论我做什么或者我去哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because no matter what I do or where I go,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:31.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你会永远和我在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you will be with me forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:36.23,中文,,0,0,0,,试图破坏我一点一滴搭建起来的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}trying to destroy every single thing that I built.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道有什么理由让我觉得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know why I thought this time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.70,中文,,0,0,0,,这一次和以往不同\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}would be any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我想让它变得不同\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wanted it to be different,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.30,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你一直让我失望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but you just keep failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:49.04,中文,,0,0,0,,所以公路旅行没戏了 是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Guess that's a no on the road trip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,公路旅行没戏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's a no on the road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,所以听卡罗琳说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So according to Caroline,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.82,中文,,0,0,0,,莎拉还没找到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sarah's still M.I.A.,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.63,中文,,0,0,0,,而现在恩佐也不知去向\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and now Enzo's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,可能在外面杀着别人的女朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Probably out killing someone else's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.33,中文,,0,0,0,,等等 你怀孕了 记得吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, uh. Pregnant, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我撒过的最愚蠢的谎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dumbest lie I've ever told.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以收回来吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can I just take that one back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.93,中文,,0,0,0,,不行 但你必须在三十年内\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, but you'll have to reinvent yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.46,中文,,0,0,0,,给自己找个新身份\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.00,中文,,0,0,0,,如果不这样的话 人们会开始问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you don't, people will start asking why
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.77,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么你没有变老\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you're not getting any older.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:24.64,中文,,0,0,0,,但当我第一次遇见你的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But when I first met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:25.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你说你已经离开神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you said you'd been away from Mystic Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.48,中文,,0,0,0,,15年了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是什么让你提前回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What made you come back ahead of schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.18,中文,,0,0,0,,像你说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我遇见了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:37.82,中文,,0,0,0,,自1864年以来 我一直是一个木匠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Since 1864, I have been a carpenter,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:40.72,中文,,0,0,0,,救护车司机 移徙工人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}an ambulance driver, a migrant worker,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.86,中文,,0,0,0,,高中生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}high-school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.56,中文,,0,0,0,,那么为什么这次是一周200块钱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So then why auto mechanic
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:47.16,中文,,0,0,0,,的汽车修理工\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for 200 bucks a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.93,中文,,0,0,0,,没有理由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 这一定很辛苦 飘荡不安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. It must be hard, all that change
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.67,中文,,0,0,0,,没有一个稳定的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without a constant in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:01.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还没谈过你哥哥的问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We haven't talked about your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.82,中文,,0,0,0,,听你把达蒙称呼成我的哥哥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A little weird to hear you refer to Damon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:07.16,中文,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}as just my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.72,中文,,0,0,0,,那我还该怎么称呼他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What else would I call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.49,中文,,0,0,0,,那我也不知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't even know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.29,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道了 那是什么意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anymore? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.85,中文,,0,0,0,,算了 这 额 这不重要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know what? It's, uh, it's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.43,中文,,0,0,0,,一切都会改变 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Things change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:20.96,中文,,0,0,0,,致改变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:23.70,中文,,0,0,0,,谁在乎其他人怎么想呢 对吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who cares what people think, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:25.49,中文,,0,0,0,,致改变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:30.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么像个神经病一样来回走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're wandering around like a crazy man why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:33.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我在找那个正确的位置\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm looking for the exact right spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:35.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要找到日食能量聚焦在哪一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to find where the power of the eclipse is focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:38.07,中文,,0,0,0,,你原本可以一开始告诉我们你有运星\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You could've just shown us the Ascendant to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:40.24,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 但我想感受一下你手放在我胸口的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, but I wanted to feel your hand on my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:42.01,中文,,0,0,0,,他有点问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's something not right about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你只是不习惯有男人和你调情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're just not used to guys hitting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:45.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 我等不及离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, I can't wait to get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:47.65,中文,,0,0,0,,和其他人说说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and talk to somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.52,中文,,0,0,0,,在那白痴用那玩意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can we just have a few lasting seconds of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:51.09,中文,,0,0,0,,将星星排成一列的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}while this idiot uses that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:54.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能停战几分钟吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to get the stars to align?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.60,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 探索自然探索得怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. What's up with the nature walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我用运星找到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I used the Ascendant to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:05.94,中文,,0,0,0,,在日食期间我们应该站立的位置\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}where we need to be standing during the eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了 让我们施些魔法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great. Let's do some magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:08.57,中文,,0,0,0,,离开这个鬼地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-俄勒冈州 -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}-Oregon. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我已经把这份报纸读了上千次了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've read this paper, like, a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:13.88,中文,,0,0,0,,那里有些关于俄勒冈州的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's something in it about Oregon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.88,0:23:15.54,中文,,0,0,0,,那里说了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 卡伊说他有很多兄弟姐妹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, Kai said he had all those brothers and sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.21,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:21.78,中文,,0,0,0,,“一家庭在波特兰惨遭屠杀”\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Family massacred in Portland"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:23.88,中文,,0,0,0,,唯一失踪的就是长子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The only one missing was the oldest boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.59,中文,,0,0,0,,叫做玛拉基的22岁青年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a 22-year-old named Malachai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.88,中文,,0,0,0,,谁会给一个孩子起这种名啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who names a kid Malachai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.93,中文,,0,0,0,,就好像他们希望我变成恶魔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's like they expected me to be evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:31.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那些孩子都被杀死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All these kids were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:33.40,中文,,0,0,0,,没看到吗 不是所有人都死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello? Not everyone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我还是挺疼爱其中一个妹妹的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had a soft spot for one of my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.57,0:23:37.03,中文,,0,0,0,,不然我早就把她的肺也挖出来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Otherwise, I would have cut her lungs out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:38.74,中文,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是脾脏了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and not just her spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.91,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:41.34,中文,,0,0,0,,没有脾脏你也能活下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can survive without a spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:42.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么觉得你好像不是在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Something tells me you're not speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.55,中文,,0,0,0,,开玩笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.98,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 这两个 我 额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, these two, I, uh, hung
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:49.32,中文,,0,0,0,,吊死在楼梯栏杆上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}off a stairwell railing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.49,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我在她腹部开了一枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then I put a hunting knife in her abdomen,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.19,中文,,0,0,0,,而他 被我淹死在游泳池里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and him I drowned in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:55.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他一直在反抗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He kept fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:56.83,中文,,0,0,0,,我当时在想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:02.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我把你留到最后才杀死 你这个不懂感恩的小东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I saved you for last, you ungrateful little"...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.07,中文,,0,0,0,,总之 就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anyway, that was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你杀了你全家人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You just killed your whole family?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:08.67,中文,,0,0,0,,准确点说是 巫师会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Coven to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:11.01,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 你知道的 全家都是巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, you know, a family of witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:13.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你让她来回折腾那么久 结果你就是个巫师\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've been making her jump through hoops, and you're a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.02,0:24:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,差不多是这样 很明显我没有力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sort of yeah. No powers obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:20.90,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 当然了 双子座巫师会听说了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, and of course, Gemini coven did not
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:23.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我的所作所为之后不是很高兴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}take it too well when they heard what I did in Portland.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:25.63,中文,,0,0,0,,所以他们把我流放到这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's why they banished me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.64,0:24:28.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这地方是个监狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This place is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.01,0:24:30.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他们为了你而设的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They created it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:35.08,中文,,0,0,0,,没错 这不是你的地狱 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yep! This isn't your hell, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:36.35,中文,,0,0,0,,是我的地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:49.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你还说这是场公平的打斗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You call this a fair fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.28,0:24:51.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你都能算是个吸血鬼祖先了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're basically an Original vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:24:55.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你杀死过一个吸血鬼祖先\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You've killed an Original before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.04,0:24:56.58,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你快给我认真\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now get your head in the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.58,0:24:58.58,中文,,0,0,0,,或许你能释放点力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and maybe you'll keep it out of the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.22,0:25:03.72,中文,,0,0,0,,高兴了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.72,0:25:04.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我在试着帮你振作起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am trying to help you pull yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.82,0:25:06.18,中文,,0,0,0,,杰里米\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}together, Jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你的问题是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now what is your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.92,0:25:09.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我的问题是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My problem
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.62,0:25:12.29,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人都认为我不应该出问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is that everyone thinks that I shouldn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.30,0:25:13.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我现在有权利过得很糟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have the right to be messed up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.76,0:25:15.63,中文,,0,0,0,,邦妮死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bonnie is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.63,0:25:16.86,中文,,0,0,0,,她知道我会这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She knew it was gonna happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.86,0:25:18.96,中文,,0,0,0,,她还用电话道的别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and she said good-bye over the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.96,0:25:21.12,中文,,0,0,0,,就为了你能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just so you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:22.79,中文,,0,0,0,,继续说啊 为了我什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep going. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.79,0:25:24.96,中文,,0,0,0,,就为了我能复活 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I could come back to life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:28.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你 埃琳娜 斯特凡 泰勒 恩佐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You, Elena, Stefan, Tyler, Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:31.16,中文,,0,0,0,,她救了所有人 除了她自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She saved everybody but herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.16,0:25:33.83,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 杰里米 你想想谈谈什么是怨恨吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen, Jeremy. You want to talk about resentment, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.83,0:25:35.29,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.30,0:25:37.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我的妻子离我而去 就因为她宁愿当个吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My wife ran away because she would rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.97,0:25:40.81,中文,,0,0,0,,也不愿做我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a vampire than be married to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.81,0:25:42.84,中文,,0,0,0,,结果发现 是达蒙将她变成吸血鬼的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come to find out, it was Damon who turned her,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.58,中文,,0,0,0,,然后她死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.58,0:25:47.58,中文,,0,0,0,,然后是珍娜 她也死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then Jenna-- she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.58,0:25:48.78,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我也死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then I died,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.79,0:25:51.25,中文,,0,0,0,,然后杀了我妻子的那个人也死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then the guy who killed my wife died,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:53.09,中文,,0,0,0,,而我其实还有点想他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I actually kind of miss him,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.09,0:25:55.49,中文,,0,0,0,,而现在我还不能和一个女孩说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and now I can't even talk to a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.50,0:25:58.63,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我一直想要咬断她的脖子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}without fantasizing about tearing into her neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.63,0:26:03.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我想说的是 杰里米 我怨恨了很多年 很多年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, Jeremy, I have resentment for years, years!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.77,0:26:06.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我能懂 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I get it, ok,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.27,0:26:07.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我找到了继续生活的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I find a way to keep going
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.84,0:26:09.47,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们都这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because that's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.47,0:26:12.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会找到了继续生活的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We find a way to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.68,0:26:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.03,0:26:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.63,0:26:27.63,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.63,0:26:30.37,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们30年之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So if we were to run into each other
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:32.84,中文,,0,0,0,,在某个小镇遇见对方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in some random town in 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.84,0:26:34.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会假装我们是陌生人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}do we pretend like we're strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.38,0:26:37.14,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 我在避开神秘瀑布镇 不是避开你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Elena, I'm avoiding Mystic Falls, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.14,0:26:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们能够聊天 能够串门\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We can talk, we can visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.82,0:26:42.05,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你还需要一名汽车修理工\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and if you ever need a car repair,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.05,0:26:45.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我会把零件以成本价卖给你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will give you the parts at cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:53.56,中文,,0,0,0,,再见 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bye, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.57,0:26:55.04,中文,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:07.22,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 先生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.03,0:27:13.56,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.56,0:27:16.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我注意到你没有祝福我的订婚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Noticed you weren't celebrating my engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.20,0:27:18.90,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:20.33,中文,,0,0,0,,很难为了一个把我弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hard to be happy for the guy who put
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.33,0:27:21.67,中文,,0,0,0,,打得送进医院的男人而高兴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}my brother in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.67,0:27:23.60,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 对的 对的 对的 好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Right, right, right. Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:25.34,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 提醒我一下 是哪个家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Remind me. Which guy was it--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:26.97,中文,,0,0,0,,断了鼻子的还是骨折的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}broken nose or fractured arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:29.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我有点喝醉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was kind of drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:30.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我还在等着你恭喜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm still waiting for the congrats
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.91,0:27:33.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我的订婚呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on my engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.21,0:27:36.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我真的为你感到高兴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I'm really happy for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.75,0:27:38.25,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.56,0:27:43.40,中文,,0,0,0,,呵 呵 你就这本事吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Heh heh. That all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.40,0:27:45.47,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧 小子 打我啊 来啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on, man. Hit me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.61,0:27:58.64,中文,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.42,0:28:03.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你就喜欢这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You frigging enjoying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:07.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你这变态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sick freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.33,0:28:08.96,中文,,0,0,0,,回家 清理\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go home, clean up,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.96,0:28:11.12,中文,,0,0,0,,忘了这曾发生的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and forget this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:16.90,中文,,0,0,0,,你到底在干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:23.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能让凯伊离开这里 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're not letting Kai out of here, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.27,0:28:24.64,中文,,0,0,0,,他刚说了他是一个连环杀手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He just said he's a serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.64,0:28:26.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 我想要离开这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't care. I want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.73,0:28:28.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能不在乎 可能是因为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How can you not care? Maybe because of all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.34,0:28:30.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你所做的那些可怕的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the horrible things you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.14,0:28:31.68,中文,,0,0,0,,可能因为杀了一群孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe because killing a bunch of kids
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:32.97,中文,,0,0,0,,对于一个杀了孕妇的人来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}is not a big deal to someone who's murdered
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:35.47,中文,,0,0,0,,不是什么大问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a pregnant woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.48,0:28:37.01,中文,,0,0,0,,我错了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.85,0:28:44.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你没把门关上吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you leave the door open?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.68,0:28:46.79,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.02,0:28:58.23,中文,,0,0,0,,这日食派对好逊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This eclipse party blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.23,0:29:01.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我穿过院子的时候 我一点都没看到太阳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't see the sun at all when I made it across the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:03.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你忘了当我们吸食人血的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You forget how much stronger we are
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.17,0:29:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有多么强大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when we drink human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:07.14,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.14,0:29:08.27,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙 请别伤害她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon, please don't hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.28,0:29:10.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我想要回我的戒指 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want my ring back, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.52,0:29:16.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:18.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我永远都摆脱不了你 是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm never gonna be rid of you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.59,0:29:21.49,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 你摆脱不了了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. No, you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.49,0:29:23.52,中文,,0,0,0,,因为在1912年我告诉了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because in 1912 I showed you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,你是谁 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who you were, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.80,0:29:27.46,中文,,0,0,0,,在1942年 我给了你你想要的自由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In 1942, I gave you your freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:29.90,中文,,0,0,0,,在1977年 我差点杀了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and in 1977, I almost killed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:31.46,中文,,0,0,0,,你最好的朋友 因为你才应该是那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}your best friend because it should have been you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:33.17,中文,,0,0,0,,在那儿帮助我的人 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}there to help me, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.17,0:29:35.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你欠我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You owe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我要你用永世\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and it'll take you an eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.70,0:29:40.01,中文,,0,0,0,,来偿还\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.17,0:29:44.51,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.41,0:29:51.01,中文,,0,0,0,,永远痛苦吧 兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}An eternity of misery, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.01,0:29:53.08,中文,,0,0,0,,就像我承诺过的一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}just like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:07.68,中文,,0,0,0,,哎呦 我可怜的外甥扎克叔叔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ouch. Poor nephew uncle Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:11.31,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡强迫扎克叔叔忘记了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan compelled uncle Zach to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.31,0:30:13.21,中文,,0,0,0,,他的女友和孩子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}about the girlfriend and the baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.22,0:30:15.51,中文,,0,0,0,,但是他无法掩盖掉所有的凶案\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but he couldn't cover up all those murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.51,0:30:17.01,中文,,0,0,0,,创建者协会重新组建了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The founders' council was restarted,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.01,0:30:19.28,中文,,0,0,0,,但斯特凡走了 离开了神秘瀑布镇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and Stefan took off, left Mystic Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.28,0:30:20.31,中文,,0,0,0,,走了大概15年\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for about 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.32,0:30:22.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We both did,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.15,0:30:23.65,中文,,0,0,0,,当我再次看到扎克叔叔的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then when I saw uncle Zach again,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:24.78,中文,,0,0,0,,每当我看着他就忍不住想起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I couldn't look at him without remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.78,0:30:26.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾经毁过的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I had ruined everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:30.11,中文,,0,0,0,,所以当我杀了他 我感到了真正的解脱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so it was a nice relief when I got to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.12,0:30:31.48,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 现在我们能回去了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. Can we go back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.48,0:30:32.62,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 来吧 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, come on, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.62,0:30:33.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你想回家和你的朋友在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You want to go home to your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.92,0:30:35.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我想回去让剩下的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want to go back and give the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.78,0:30:38.69,中文,,0,0,0,,双子座巫师们痛苦地死去 双赢啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the Gemini coven an excruciating death. Win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.69,0:30:40.62,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说 我知道这个人不是一个模范公民 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. I know this guy's not a model citizen, ok, Bonnie,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.63,0:30:42.13,中文,,0,0,0,,但我得回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I got to get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.13,0:30:45.40,中文,,0,0,0,,不只是为了埃琳娜 也是为了我的弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not just for Elena but for my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.40,0:30:47.97,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry, Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.97,0:30:51.00,中文,,0,0,0,,道歉对我没有用\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry doesn't work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.00,0:30:53.34,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们可能有一些分歧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. We might be having a bit of a disagreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.34,0:30:56.31,中文,,0,0,0,,但不要对她动手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but don't ever lay a hand on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.31,0:30:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,现在不是争论这个的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kind of a nonissue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.92,0:31:00.52,中文,,0,0,0,,错过了今天的日食\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Missed today's eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.52,0:31:01.75,中文,,0,0,0,,推迟到明天吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rain check for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.75,0:31:03.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.23,0:31:12.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你和警长似乎相处得不太好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you and the sheriff don't seem to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.16,0:31:15.66,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 利兹和我太太高中时是竞争对手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh. Liz and my wife were high-school rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.67,0:31:17.96,中文,,0,0,0,,争的是谁是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}some issue about who was captain
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.96,0:31:19.57,中文,,0,0,0,,曲棍球队队长\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of the field hockey team.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.57,0:31:21.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你结婚了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're married?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.24,0:31:23.14,中文,,0,0,0,,曾经是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.14,0:31:26.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 克里斯在车祸中去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Kris died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:27.91,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.91,0:31:31.38,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 这就是我离开神秘瀑布镇的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, that's why I left Mystic Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.38,0:31:36.02,中文,,0,0,0,,太多回忆了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Too many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.02,0:31:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你和警长说了些杰伊的什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what'd you tell the sheriff about Jay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.19,0:31:41.06,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 就说我看到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, just what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.06,0:31:43.43,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 大量的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, tons of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.43,0:31:46.03,中文,,0,0,0,,可能是一只美洲狮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Probably a mountain lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.03,0:31:49.97,中文,,0,0,0,,只是另一起动物的攻击 是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just another animal attack, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.97,0:31:52.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你听起来很怀疑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sound doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.78,0:31:55.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这或许听起来很奇怪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is gonna sound weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.41,0:31:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,但是昨天晚上 杰伊告诉我他正在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but last night, Jay told me that he was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.28,0:32:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,跟踪一只吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}tracking a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.48,0:32:06.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 这很疯狂 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, that's crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.15,0:32:08.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我要告诉你一些事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm gonna show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.39,0:32:12.59,中文,,0,0,0,,我以为你同意离开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought you agreed to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.59,0:32:15.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我忘了拿外套 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I forgot my jacket, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.09,0:32:17.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那个人怎么回事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What happened with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.03,0:32:18.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你我自有一套方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you I have a system.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.56,0:32:20.89,中文,,0,0,0,,让某个人揍你一顿这样你才有感觉吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Letting somebody kick your ass so that you can feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你是最没资格说教我的处理机制\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You are the last person who should be lecturing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.30,0:32:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,的那个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}me on coping mechanisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:28.13,中文,,0,0,0,,不是只有你一个人悲伤 斯特凡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're not alone in your grief, Stefan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.14,0:32:30.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你失去达蒙的时候 我失去了邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I lost Bonnie when you lost Damon,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:31.70,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我熬过来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I fought through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.70,0:32:32.80,中文,,0,0,0,,是吗 靠你一个人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah? All by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:34.77,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.77,0:32:38.67,中文,,0,0,0,,那是很艰难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And it was hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.67,0:32:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你拒我于千里之外\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know that you're pushing me away
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.04,0:32:41.70,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我从来不喜欢达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because I never liked Damon--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.71,0:32:43.47,中文,,0,0,0,,相信我 不是这样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Believe me, that's not what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.48,0:32:45.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道他是你的兄弟 我明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I know that he's your brother. I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.28,0:32:48.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但你为什么要为了这么讨厌的一个人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but why inflict so much pain on yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.92,0:32:51.82,中文,,0,0,0,,让自己忍受那么多痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for such a hateful person?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.82,0:32:53.62,中文,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 他不值得你悲伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I mean, he doesn't deserve your grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.62,0:32:56.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你还有其他方法可以重新生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's got to be another way that you can move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.73,0:32:57.99,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 我只是不能像你一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry that I can't just forget him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.00,0:32:59.86,中文,,0,0,0,,忘了他 埃琳娜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}like you, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.86,0:33:00.93,中文,,0,0,0,,没有人忘了他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No one's forgetting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:02.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你忘了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.33,0:33:03.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你抹去了关于他的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You erased him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.67,0:33:05.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.10,0:33:06.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你让阿拉里克催眠你去忘记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You had Alaric compel you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.40,0:33:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙做过的所有的美好的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}every good thing that Damon ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.44,0:33:09.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你让他变成了你心目中的禽兽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You made him a monster in your own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.88,0:33:11.10,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你无法承受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because you couldn't handle the grief
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.11,0:33:12.67,中文,,0,0,0,,失去他的悲伤\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:14.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我不相信你所说的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't believe anything that you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.14,0:33:15.30,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么我要那么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.30,0:33:16.41,中文,,0,0,0,,因为你深爱着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because you were in love with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:17.77,中文,,0,0,0,,并且他也深爱着你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and he was in love with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.78,0:33:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,当达蒙死了的时候 一部分的你也死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and when Damon died, a part of you died, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.68,0:33:24.78,中文,,0,0,0,,哇 哦 天哪 什么 不 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wow. Oh, God. What? No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.79,0:33:28.82,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 我怎么可能爱上达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan, how could I possibly love Damon?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.82,0:33:30.22,中文,,0,0,0,,相信我 很长一段时间以来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Believe me, I asked myself that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我也在问自己这个问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for a very long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.96,0:33:33.83,中文,,0,0,0,,最终 我懂了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and then eventually, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.83,0:33:35.50,中文,,0,0,0,,达蒙唤醒了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damon inspired you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:39.11,中文,,0,0,0,,他促使你接受你内心最黑暗的部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}he pushed you to own the darkest parts of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.11,0:33:40.84,中文,,0,0,0,,当你死了的时候 他是唯一一个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and when you died, he was the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.85,0:33:42.04,中文,,0,0,0,,能让你再次感到活力的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that could make you feel alive again,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.05,0:33:44.71,中文,,0,0,0,,而你让他感觉到人性\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and you made him feel human.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.72,0:33:46.42,中文,,0,0,0,,你爱达蒙 和我爱他的理由\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You love Damon for the same reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.42,0:33:48.22,中文,,0,0,0,,是一样的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I love Damon
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.22,0:33:49.85,中文,,0,0,0,,因为尽管他做过那么多事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because in spite of every single thing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.85,0:33:53.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们离不开他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that he did we couldn't live without him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.83,0:33:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你不需要这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and now you don't have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.52,0:33:56.89,中文,,0,0,0,,但我还要承受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.89,0:34:00.70,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我要用我的方式去做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I'm gonna do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你就按你的方式做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can do it yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.30,0:34:23.83,中文,,0,0,0,,这是哪里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.83,0:34:26.66,中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.67,0:34:31.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我只与我信任的人分享秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A secret I only share with people I trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.97,0:34:36.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你记得那个夏天镇上的天然气泄漏吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You remember the gas leak in town over the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.17,0:34:38.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我回来确认我的祖母是否平安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, I came back to make sure my grandmother was ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.34,0:34:40.60,中文,,0,0,0,,那么多年来我第一次回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First time I've been back in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.61,0:34:43.28,中文,,0,0,0,,当我穿过镇的边界的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When I crossed the town border...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.98,0:34:47.12,中文,,0,0,0,,一些东西改变了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.12,0:34:52.22,中文,,0,0,0,,回忆如潮水般涌来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Memories came flooding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.23,0:34:56.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我意识到我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I realized that my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.03,0:34:58.96,中文,,0,0,0,,不是在车祸中死去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}didn't die in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.97,0:35:00.80,中文,,0,0,0,,她是被谋杀的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She was murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.81,0:35:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,在我面前被吸干了血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}drained of her blood right in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.44,0:35:07.21,中文,,0,0,0,,那个杀人者让我相信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the killer made me believe
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.21,0:35:09.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我要为她的死负责\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.18,0:35:12.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我要找出是什么怪物\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had to find out what kind of monster
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.41,0:35:14.71,中文,,0,0,0,,能够这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}could do all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.51,0:35:26.35,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Vampires--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.35,0:35:27.89,中文,,0,0,0,,他们真的存在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}they are real,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.89,0:35:31.85,中文,,0,0,0,,而其中一只吸血鬼杀死了我妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and one murdered my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.85,0:35:34.39,中文,,0,0,0,,但是这只\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but this is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.39,0:35:36.76,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了杰伊的吸血鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who murdered Jay,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让他说出他所有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I'm gonna get him to name all
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.20,0:35:39.67,中文,,0,0,0,,吸血鬼同伴的名字\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}his vampire buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.67,0:35:43.23,中文,,0,0,0,,从那只咬了你的朋友莎拉的吸血鬼开始\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}starting with the one who bit your friend Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:51.01,中文,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.02,0:35:52.35,中文,,0,0,0,,你要是敢动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You try anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.35,0:35:54.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我会报警向全世界揭露\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I call 911 and out your vampire sister
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.52,0:35:55.82,中文,,0,0,0,,你的吸血鬼姐姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:58.73,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 放轻松 你想怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Just take it easy. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.89,0:36:04.32,中文,,0,0,0,,答案 我昨晚整理房子的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Answers. I found this when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.32,0:36:07.16,中文,,0,0,0,,发现了这张照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}tossing the house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.16,0:36:09.39,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我的妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.39,0:36:11.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我能认出来的原因是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and the reason I know this is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.29,0:36:14.42,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我从小就有了这张照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}because I've had this since I was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.93,0:36:20.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我妈妈是个无名氏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My mom was a Jane Doe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.56,0:36:21.83,中文,,0,0,0,,当他们把有6个月身孕的她遗弃在医院的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her body was still warm when they dumped it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.83,0:36:24.76,中文,,0,0,0,,她的身体依旧温暖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}at the hospital 6 months pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:27.83,中文,,0,0,0,,护士认为我也在送达医院前死亡了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The nurses thought I was DOA, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.83,0:36:29.53,中文,,0,0,0,,但是一位医生做了紧急破腹产\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but one doctor did an emergency C-section,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.53,0:36:31.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我活了下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.71,0:36:34.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我在育婴箱里生活了3个月\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I lived 3 months in an Incubator.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.40,0:36:37.24,中文,,0,0,0,,他们不知道谁是我的爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They didn't know who my dad was,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.24,0:36:38.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and neither did I,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.38,0:36:39.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我找到了这张照片\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but then I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.55,0:36:50.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你的爸爸是扎克·塞尔瓦托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your dad is Zach Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.79,0:36:57.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能就这样毁了我人生中这一整章节的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How could you obliterate an entire chapter of my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.29,0:37:01.59,中文,,0,0,0,,埃琳娜 虽然我也很想认为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, Elena. As much as I like to think
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.60,0:37:03.43,中文,,0,0,0,,自己充满智慧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I am full of wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.43,0:37:04.99,中文,,0,0,0,,但我想我们是时候停止\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think it's time we stop pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.00,0:37:08.36,中文,,0,0,0,,假装我知道什么是最好的了 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that I actually know what's best, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.36,0:37:10.29,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说 我现在把我自己的问题理清楚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. I've got my own issues to sort out right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.30,0:37:14.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我认为这个能够比我自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I think this will explain it much better
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.80,0:37:16.27,中文,,0,0,0,,解释得更清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.10,0:37:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,亲爱的自己 如果你正在读这话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Dear me, if you're reading this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.67,0:37:35.90,中文,,0,0,0,,那么有人泄露了这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Then somebody spilled the beans
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.90,0:37:37.97,中文,,0,0,0,,关于你选择性的失忆的秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"About your selective memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.97,0:37:40.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我的钱在卡罗琳那\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"My money's on Caroline.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:43.77,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 你爱达蒙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Yes, you loved Damon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.77,0:37:48.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你耗尽全部的激情爱着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"You loved him with a passion that consumed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.65,0:37:49.94,中文,,0,0,0,,而当达蒙去世的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"And then when Damon died,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.94,0:37:55.34,中文,,0,0,0,,他留下的伤痕太深 太痛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"The void he filled was too deep, too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.35,0:37:56.74,中文,,0,0,0,,和你的灵魂伴侣面对永生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Facing an eternity with your soul mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.74,0:37:58.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你贸然行事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"You went off the deep end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.18,0:38:01.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你变成了你不想成为的那种人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"You turned into someone that you weren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:04.65,中文,,0,0,0,,一个魔鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"A monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.65,0:38:06.42,中文,,0,0,0,,阿拉里克能恢复你失去的记忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Alaric can restore your lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.42,0:38:08.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你只需要开口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"All you have to do is ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.99,0:38:11.25,中文,,0,0,0,,但我希望你别这么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"But I hope that you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.25,0:38:14.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我尝试过别的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I tried it the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.23,0:38:16.66,中文,,0,0,0,,我没能使痛苦结束\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I didn't see an end to the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.03,0:38:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你能重新发现自我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I want you to rediscover yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.70,0:38:24.17,中文,,0,0,0,,就算没有那个让你认识自己的人在身边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"In the absence of the one who defined you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.17,0:38:25.80,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你对未来有任何一点希望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"If you feel any hope for the future at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.81,0:38:28.14,中文,,0,0,0,,那么你已经开始好转\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Then you're already better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.51,0:38:36.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你得到了一个重新开始的机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"You've been given a chance to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.18,0:38:38.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你好好把握它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I want you to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.75,0:38:41.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你开心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want you to be happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.39,0:38:44.56,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你想我怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:38:59.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你能先收着它吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can you hold on to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.70,0:39:03.26,中文,,0,0,0,,好好放着 以免我需要再读一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}keep it safe in case I ever need to read it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.57,0:39:12.07,中文,,0,0,0,,因为羞耻来吃东西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shame eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.08,0:39:14.64,中文,,0,0,0,,在想着那个怀孕的女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thinking about that pregnant lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.65,0:39:17.58,中文,,0,0,0,,她喜欢吃煎饼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She had a thing for pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.58,0:39:18.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你就记得这些吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's what you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.88,0:39:21.75,中文,,0,0,0,,你记得 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You remember it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.76,0:39:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你每天都做煎饼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You make pancakes every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:25.79,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我无聊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.79,0:39:29.56,中文,,0,0,0,,不 因为你在惩罚你自己\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Because you're punishing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.56,0:39:30.66,中文,,0,0,0,,你把这里称为你的地狱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You called this place your hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.66,0:39:33.69,中文,,0,0,0,,那意味着你感到悔恨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That means you feel remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.69,0:39:38.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这是你与卡伊不同的原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's what makes you different than Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.16,0:39:42.33,中文,,0,0,0,,这意味着你还有希望\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It means there's hope for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.33,0:39:46.56,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我们还可以离开这里 邦妮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look. We can still get out of here, Bonnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.57,0:39:48.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以把运星那个装置偷过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We can just steal that Ascendant contraption,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.30,0:39:49.70,中文,,0,0,0,,搞清楚凯伊知道些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}find out what Kai knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.70,0:39:50.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我们抛下他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll ditch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.90,0:39:52.26,中文,,0,0,0,,反正他也没有任何力量\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He doesn't have any powers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.26,0:39:54.36,中文,,0,0,0,,事实上没这么简单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Actually, it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.37,0:39:57.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你还再别那样做 这很吓人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got to stop doing that. It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.03,0:40:01.07,中文,,0,0,0,,是这样的 我有特殊的魔法效应\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here's the thing. I have a peculiar effect on magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.07,0:40:02.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能自己施展魔法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't generate it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.94,0:40:07.91,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我能暂时从别的东西上吸取一点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I can consume it from others temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.91,0:40:10.75,中文,,0,0,0,,家人都叫我讨厌鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Family called me an abomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.75,0:40:13.15,中文,,0,0,0,,那太伤我感情了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That hurt my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.15,0:40:14.62,中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.40,0:40:20.83,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们知道了 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok. We get it. Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.33,0:40:26.93,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么巫师会和我相处不来了吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can see why my coven and I didn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.93,0:40:28.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我闻到了最后通牒的气息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I smell an ultimatum.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:31.94,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我消耗了邦妮所有的魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I consume all of Bonnie's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.94,0:40:35.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我就会杀了她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am just gonna end up killing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.31,0:40:37.44,中文,,0,0,0,,但是如果我们合作\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but if we work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.44,0:40:40.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就可以友好地一起回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we can all go home as friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.98,0:40:42.62,中文,,0,0,0,,或者我可以吞噬她的魔力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or I can devour her magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.62,0:40:45.25,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了你们俩再独自回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}kill you both and go home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.06,0:40:50.60,中文,,0,0,0,,那会是怎样呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.53,0:41:13.29,中文,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.70,0:41:28.99,中文,,0,0,0,,艾薇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.00,0:41:33.03,中文,,0,0,0,,斯特凡 我感觉很不好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stefan, I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.03,0:41:34.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你的朋友恩佐让我喝他的血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your friend Enzo made me drink his blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.83,0:41:38.00,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我非常饥渴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and now I'm just so thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.03,0:41:45.53,中文,,0,0,0,,
